<actions>
  <update-node tree="member_expression: _getEpochId().sub [1851,1868]" label="_getEpochId().add" />
  <update-node tree="member_expression: _totalAmountPerEpoch         .mul(_getUserBalancePerEpoch(msg.sender, epochId))         .div [4857,4949]" label="_totalAmountPerEpoch         .mul(_getUserBalancePerEpoch(msg.sender, epochId))         .mul" />
  <update-node tree="member_expression: TOTAL_DISTRIBUTED_AMOUNT.mul(10**18).div [1572,1612]" label="TOTAL_DISTRIBUTED_AMOUNT.mul(10**18).mul" />
  <update-node tree="member_expression: lastEpochIdHarvested[msg.sender].add [2823,2859]" label="lastEpochIdHarvested[msg.sender].sub" />
  <update-node tree="member_expression: lastInitializedEpoch.add [3919,3943]" label="lastInitializedEpoch.sub" />
  <update-node tree="member_expression: block.timestamp.sub(epochStart).div(epochDuration).add [5672,5726]" label="block.timestamp.sub(epochStart).div(epochDuration).sub" />
</actions>
